Title: OMD user cannot do --scan-parents
Component: core
Benefit: 1
State: open
Cost: 2
Date: 2011-09-08 10:20:21
Class: nastiness

As an OMD user you cannot always do a parent scan since
traceroute might miss the SUID bit. We could make the
command configurable in main.mk and maybe prepare OMD
such that it always works correctly...
